" Fugitive {{{

" Use git inside of vim
Bundle 'tpope/vim-fugitive'

augroup fugitive
  autocmd!
  " Auto-clean fugitive buffers
  autocmd BufReadPost fugitive://* set bufhidden=delete
augroup END

" }}}

